鄰居質素差？<br />\n公屋仔就係逗緊政府每年6萬元福利既寄生蟲<br />\n有冇人係愛黨不愛國?<br />\n收1000遊行根本冇問題<br />\n由公屋申請入息限額分析公屋人質素<br />\n講真其實公屋仔有咩資格批評政府?<br />\n其實公屋仔同綜援蝗蟲心態上有咩分別？<br />\n窮=失敗 社會唔應該同情失敗既人<br />\n有冇人支持廢除電車？"},{"pid":"5eb9c3384de4bacace224a52803290787e08b532","tid":302534,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"搵嚟搞<br />\n貼埋d圖on9當有趣"},{"pid":"3211c2ab6d40f00faa8d01a620c3dfbde2b44fbf","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc33d86f2ef28efa0cacb75a1b54ce5201adafb6","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d36040efb52ac30c3e8e2b21fca5c59e9399879e","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:57:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd33a2edbf512ffc1e6416af2f0d08e1495f9719","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:42:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84ad6e3d09a9f9685fc68e3e711f2eed72a0d210","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:19:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be5aa7282a617fcb56863e75930609540617f4a1","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17ffef9f7a4c12a1d9763ae4aef7fab1213e3d3d","tid":302534,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"班仆街陷家剷永世貧賤中國人不得移民"},{"pid":"cd0019e4928c40edd30fe89120be01424f75ad4c","tid":302534,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"三色貓 天才小釣手 奶波魔"},{"pid":"c475e6ea0f499ed40f4a17e0c9ddc2e7b40e7f44","tid":302534,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"優美開始 十卜ching"},{"pid":"2ca79d51b6716fc234441a9081f1