6a","tid":302534,"uid":42452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"有啲打字好接近香港人，但有時都會走漏眼打左啲大陸字，而且佢哋說話比一般五毛有攻擊性好多，可能係特種五毛都未頂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca41b7421b65a97bc6f9b85dac0d140b0d448b40","tid":302534,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"原來都有巴打確認到某啲「打字好香港」嘅大陸五毛，厲害！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋用開嘅係廣東粵語，所以有時會打類似唸(諗)，瞓(訓)。<br />\n喱點我唔太確定，瞓字可能先係正確，但正所謂約定俗成，香港人打開訓，我未見過人打瞓，係近兩三年開始見高登有喱類大陸字。<br />\n不過如果喱班人唔係狂踩香港捧大陸，有大陸衰嘢嘅新聞又拉埋香港人落水，我係唔會介意佢哋係咪大陸人。"},{"pid":"bd6937e5324ad2b56e0479783917c32299386537","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4a9ff92c8f78369af7e667c8bddaed9482659ff","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"003edb039345a71f8094e3b461008a1b37470f43","tid":302534,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee06a49722555acbc9fa18a902b00d8de052e043","tid":302534,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:40:58.000Z","msg":"兔仔識得留名遲啲覆 一定係專業打手<br />\n仲識得平時扮吓支持抗爭者"},{"pid":"47e6f10bd0899bcdac7f4744fbedc1e85a7c557e","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a916afa7062d49b031809957d36ecb81730cb36","tid":302534,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a4e17b7a2d09446c748d96ebe3b1298179370ad","tid":302534,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T